<h2 id="models">Models</h2>
<h3 id="posts">Posts</h3>
<p>The posts model is in <code>app/models/post.rb</code></p>
<p>The model for the posts has a <code>has_many</code> association for the comments so they get assigned to the  sepcific post. The model also has the word count and reading time methods to display on the front end.</p>
